---
import Link from "../components/Link.astro";
import ContentPageLayout from "../layouts/ContentPageLayout.astro";
import DefaultLayout from "../layouts/DefaultLayout.astro";
---

<DefaultLayout title="Join Us" image="/target-3.jpg">
  <div class="prose-lg">
    <p>
      To join Pinner Archers archery club you need to have completed an AGB
      approved beginners course (see our
      <Link href="/courses">beginner courses</Link>) or have been a member of
      another archery club. Membership to Pinner Archers is subject to an
      evaluation of competence at shooting; this may be by way of demonstration
      or certification indicating completion of a recognised beginners course.
    </p>
    <p>Our membership is divided in two parts.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row">
      <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-2xl md:flex-1">
        <h3>Pinner Archers Archery Club Membership</h3>
        <p>
          Pinner Archers Club fees run from 1st September to 31st August and
          include affiliations to AGB, SCAS & MCAA. The Fees are payable to the
          Pinner Archers Treasurer.
        </p>
        <p>
          Membership of Pinner Archers archery club is conditional on the
          applicant being a current member of the Tithe Farm Sports & Social
          Club. Once approved the applicant(s) can submit a membership form to
          Pinner Archers with the appropriate fee.
        </p>
        <p>
          Pinner Archers Club Fees 2025-2026<br />
          Adults £125<br />
          Juniors (under 21) £70<br />
          Associate (excl. AGB) £60<br />
          Joining Fee (1st Year) £15*
        </p>
        <small>
          *Beginners completing the course and wishing to become members of
          Pinner Archers will not be required to pay the joining fee.
        </small>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-2xl md:flex-1">
        <h3>Tithe Farm Sports & Social Club Membership</h3>
        <p>
          Application to Tithe Farm Sports & Social Club must be seconded by a
          Pinner Archers committee member and the appropriate fee to a TFSSC
          committee member or at the bar (on ground floor).
        </p>
        <p>
          Tithe Farm Sports & Social Club Fees<br />
          Single £45<br />
          Joint £85<br />
          Junior (under 18) £35<br />
          OAP £25
        </p>
        <p>
          The fees are payable to the Tithe Farm Sports & Social Club treasurer.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h2>Shooting Fees</h2>
    <p>
      There are no additional fees to shoot as a member of the club. Shooting
      fees are required for non-members who wish to shoot on a given day.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row">
      <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-2xl md:flex-1">
        <h3>Shooting Fees at Tithe Farm Indoor Range</h3>
        <p>
          Members of Pinner Archers no shooting fee required.<br />
          Visiting Adult or Junior £3 (with proof of AGB membership)
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-2xl md:flex-1">
        <h3>Shooting Fees at Metropolitan Bushey Sports Club Outdoor Range</h3>
        <p>
          Members of Pinner Archers no shooting fee required.<br />
          Visiting Adult £5 (with proof of AGB membership)<br />
          Visiting Junior £3 (with proof of AGB membership)
        </p>
        <p>
          NB: Shooting Fees when applicable at Tithe Farm and Metropolitan
          Bushey Sports Club ranges are to be paid to Pinner Archers.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</DefaultLayout>
